*clipper-20070907 (19 Dec 2007)

  19 Dec 2007; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  +files/20070907-as-needed.patch, +clipper-20070907.ebuild:
  Bump as a dependency of Coot 0.4 prereleases.

  30 May 2007; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  clipper-20070528.ebuild:
  Move the sed to change the includes to use clipper-2 to after the install,
  so it compiles properly. Keyword ~ppc.

*clipper-20070528 (29 May 2007)

  29 May 2007; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  +files/20070528-as-needed.patch, +metadata.xml, +clipper-20070528.ebuild:
  Add a slotted version of clipper. Version 1 is installed with ccp4-6, but we
  need version 2 for coots 0.2 and newer.

